{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PzpS91PDB4vNdcyD5zXwKV","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-START:dev-workflow-enforcement -->\n     2→\n     3→## Harness Enforcement (codeharness)\n     4→\n     5→During implementation, the agent MUST:\n     6→\n     7→### Observability\n     8→- Query VictoriaLogs after running the application to check for errors\n     9→- Verify OTLP instrumentation is active in new code paths\n    10→- Use `curl localhost:9428/select/logsql/query?query=level:error` to check for runtime errors\n    11→\n    12→### Documentation\n    13→- Create or update per-subsystem AGENTS.md for any new modules (max 100 lines)\n    14→- Update exec-plan at `docs/exec-plans/active/{story-id}.md` with progress\n    15→- Ensure inline code documentation for new public APIs\n    16→\n    17→### Testing\n    18→- Write tests AFTER implementation, BEFORE verification\n    19→- Achieve 100% project-wide test coverage\n    20→- All tests must pass before proceeding to verification\n    21→\n    22→### Verification\n    23→- Run `/harness-verify` to produce Showboat proof document\n    24→- Do NOT mark story complete without passing verification\n    25→\n    26→<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:dev-workflow-enforcement -->\n    27→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01RvA5UTbt2H8jvK22NCiBXL","session_id":"44e99ebb-e385-42dc-a684-d204e4d10303","uuid":"d16717ba-e408-4721-922f-38719e61b789","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:41:15.495Z"}
