{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DacrqVSNTahYP9frKXE8K2","type":"tool_result","content":"    61→\n    62→### 4-2-dockerfile-template-dev-integration — create-story (2026-03-21T05:42Z)\n    63→\n    64→- Expanded from 3 epic ACs to 10 for full implementation coverage\n    65→- Risk: AC #5 (generated Dockerfile passes validateDockerfile) depends on template content matching all 6 rule categories — tight coupling with Story 4.1's validator regex\n    66→- AC #3 (generic template) — existing `templates/Dockerfile.verify` uses `COPY . /workspace/` which would fail \"no source copy\" rule. Generated templates must differ.\n    67→- Init orchestrator (`init-project.ts`) is already complex; template generation delegated to new `dockerfile-template.ts` to minimize changes\n    68→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"44e99ebb-e385-42dc-a684-d204e4d10303","uuid":"e57edcd1-4770-471e-a834-651e9dcacfbb","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:49:48.845Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"\n### 4-2-dockerfile-template-dev-integration — create-story (2026-03-21T05:42Z)\n\n- Expanded from 3 epic ACs to 10 for full implementation coverage\n- Risk: AC #5 (generated Dockerfile passes validateDockerfile) depends on template content matching all 6 rule categories — tight coupling with Story 4.1's validator regex\n- AC #3 (generic template) — existing `templates/Dockerfile.verify` uses `COPY . /workspace/` which would fail \"no source copy\" rule. Generated templates must differ.\n- Init orchestrator (`init-project.ts`) is already complex; template generation delegated to new `dockerfile-template.ts` to minimize changes\n","numLines":8,"startLine":61,"totalLines":68}}}
